            <head xml:id="bHY6yh-e09874-Hd1e108">Rubrica 3</head>
            <head xml:id="bHY6yh-e09874-Hd1e111" type="question-title">De mortis naturalitate</head>
          <p xml:id="bHY6yh-e09874-d1e114">
        <lb ed="#V" n="41"/>¶ De mortis naturalitate. Rubrica. 3.
          </p>
          <p xml:id="bHY6yh-e09874-d1e119">
        <lb ed="#V" n="42"/><ref xml:id="bHY6yh-e09874-Rd1e116">IOb. Hystoria. capitulo 38.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-e09874-Qd1e123">Deficiet
        <lb ed="#V" n="43"/>omnis caro simul et 
               ho<lb ed="#V" n="44" break="no"/>mo in cinerem reuertetur.</quote> 
          </p>
          <p xml:id="bHY6yh-e09874-d1e131">
        <lb ed="#V" n="45"/>¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-e09874-Rd1e130">In genesi. capitulo 6.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-e09874-Qd1e135">Dixit deus: non per<!--325.xml-->
          <cb ed="#V" n="b"/>
        <lb ed="#V" n="46" break="no"/>manebit spiritus meus in homine in 
               eter<lb ed="#V" n="47" break="no"/>num: quia caro est.</quote>
          </p>
          <p xml:id="bHY6yh-e09874-d1e148">
        <lb ed="#V" n="48"/>¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-e09874-Rd1e149">Salomon in ecclesiaste. capitulo 2.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-e09874-Qd1e152">Moritur 
               do<lb ed="#V" n="49" break="no"/>ctus similiter vt indoctus.</quote>
          </p>
          <p xml:id="bHY6yh-e09874-d1e158"> 
      / <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-e09874-Rd1e159">3. capitulo.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-e09874-Qd1e160">Omnia 
               tem<lb ed="#V" n="50" break="no"/>pus habent: et suis spaciis transeunt 
               vniuer<lb ed="#V" n="51" break="no"/>sa sub sole.</quote>
          </p>
          <p xml:id="bHY6yh-e09874-d1e168"> 
      / <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-e09874-Rd1e171">9. capitulo.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-e09874-Qd1e170">Nemo est qui semper viuat.</quote>
          </p>
          <p xml:id="bHY6yh-e09874-d1e174">
        <lb ed="#V" n="52"/>¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-e09874-Rd1e181">Regum. libro 2. capitulo 14.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-e09874-Qd1e178">Omnes morimur<sic>::</sic> et
        <lb ed="#V" n="53"/>quasi aqua dilabimur in terram que non 
               re<lb ed="#V" n="54" break="no"/>uertuntur.</quote>
          </p>
          <p xml:id="bHY6yh-e09874-d1e186">
        <lb ed="#V" n="55"/>¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-e09874-Rd1e195">Iesus filius sirach in ecclesiastico. capitulo 40.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-e09874-Qd1e190">
               Omnia<lb ed="#V" n="56" break="no"/>que de terra sunt in terram conuertentur.</quote>
          </p>
          <p xml:id="bHY6yh-e09874-d1e196">/ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-e09874-Rd1e205">41
        <lb ed="#V" n="57"/>capitulo.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-e09874-Qd1e198">Iudicium mortis a domino omni carni.</quote>
          </p>
          <p xml:id="bHY6yh-e09874-d1e205">
        <lb ed="#V" n="58"/>¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-e09874-Rd1e219">Salustius in iugurtino:</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-e09874-Qd1e209">Omnia orta 
               occi<lb ed="#V" n="59" break="no"/>dunt. et angea senescunt.</quote>
          </p>
          <p xml:id="bHY6yh-e09874-d1e215">
        <lb ed="#V" n="60"/>¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-e09874-Rd1e231">Oratius in odis. libro 2. capitulo 18.</ref>
        <lb ed="#V" n="61"/><quote xml:id="bHY6yh-e09874-Qd1e219">Heu fugaces postume: postume
        <lb ed="#V" n="62"/>Labuntur anni: nec pietas moram
        <lb ed="#V" n="63"/>Rugi et instanti senecte
        <lb ed="#V" n="64"/>Affert indomiteque morti.</quote>
          </p>
          <p xml:id="bHY6yh-e09874-d1e231">
        <lb ed="#V" n="65"/>/ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-e09874-Rd1e249">Idem in epodo. libro i. capitulo 16. et penultimo.</ref>
        <lb ed="#V" n="66"/><quote xml:id="bHY6yh-e09874-Qd1e235">Urget diem nox: et dies noctem.</quote>
          </p>
          <p xml:id="bHY6yh-e09874-d1e241">
        <lb ed="#V" n="67"/>/ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-e09874-Rd1e261">Idem in poetria.</ref>
        <lb ed="#V" n="68"/><quote xml:id="bHY6yh-e09874-Qd1e245">Debemur morti nos nostraque.
        <lb ed="#V" n="69"/>Mortalia facta peribunt.
        <lb ed="#V" n="70"/>Nedum sermonum: sed honos et gratia viuax.</quote>
          </p>
          <p xml:id="bHY6yh-e09874-d1e255">
        <lb ed="#V" n="71"/>/ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-e09874-Rd1e277">Idem epistolarum. libro i. epistola 17.</ref>
        <lb ed="#V" n="72"/><quote xml:id="bHY6yh-e09874-Qd1e259">Mors vltima linea est rerum.</quote>
          </p>
          <p xml:id="bHY6yh-e09874-d1e265">
        <lb ed="#V" n="73"/>/ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-e09874-Rd1e289">Libro. 2. epistola 3. et finali.</ref>
        <lb ed="#V" n="74"/><quote xml:id="bHY6yh-e09874-Qd1e269">Singula de nobis anni predantur euntes.</quote>
          </p>
          <p xml:id="bHY6yh-e09874-d1e298">
        <lb ed="#V" n="75"/>¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-e09874-Rd1e302">Pylon vel phylemon. in libro sapientie. capitulo 7.</ref>
        <lb ed="#V" n="76"/><quote xml:id="bHY6yh-e09874-Qd1e306">Unus ex omnibus introitus ad vitam: et 
               si<lb ed="#V" n="77" break="no"/>milis exitus.</quote>
          </p>
          <p xml:id="bHY6yh-e09874-d1e282">
        <lb ed="#V" n="78"/>¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-e09874-Rd1e316">Ouidius de tristibus. libro 3. epistola 4.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-e09874-Qd1e286">Singula ne
        <lb ed="#V" n="79"/>referam nil non mortale tenemus.
        <lb ed="#V" n="80"/>Pectoris exceptis ingeniique bonis.</quote>
          </p>
          <p xml:id="bHY6yh-e09874-d1e294">
        <lb ed="#V" n="81"/>¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-e09874-Rd1e330">Quintilianus declamationum. libro i. 
               decla<lb ed="#V" n="82" break="no"/>matione 3.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-e09874-Qd1e298">Omnis nos hora per <sic>tacicos</sic> 
               fallen<lb ed="#V" n="83" break="no"/>tesque cursus applicat fato: et in turpissimo
        <lb ed="#V" n="84"/>perpetuitatis cogitatione destructi per 
               exi<lb ed="#V" n="85" break="no"/>gua festinantis eui momenta premorimur.</quote>
          </p>
          <p xml:id="bHY6yh-e09874-d1e310">
        <lb ed="#V" n="86"/>¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-e09874-Rd1e349">Paulus apostolus in epistola ad hebreos
        <lb ed="#V" n="87"/>capitulo 9</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-e09874-Qd1e314">Statutum est omnibus semel mori.</quote>
          </p>
          <p xml:id="bHY6yh-e09874-d1e320">
        <lb ed="#V" n="88"/>¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-e09874-Rd1e362">Seneca tragediarum in hercule furente. capitulo 7.</ref>
        <lb ed="#V" n="89"/><quote xml:id="bHY6yh-e09874-Qd1e324">Prima que vitam
        <lb ed="#V" n="90"/>Dedit hora carpsit.</quote> <!--326.xml-->
          </p>
          <p xml:id="bHY6yh-e09874-d1e338">
              <pb ed="#V" n="144-r"/>
              <cb ed="#V" n="a"/>
        <lb ed="#V" n="1"/>/ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-e09874-Rd1e382">In troa. capitulo 5.</ref>
        <lb ed="#V" n="2"/><quote xml:id="bHY6yh-e09874-Qd1e342">Tempus nos auidum deuorat.</quote>
          </p>
          <p xml:id="bHY6yh-e09874-d1e348">
        <lb ed="#V" n="3"/>/ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-e09874-Rd1e396">Idem epistolarum ad lucillum. libro 4. epistola 3.</ref>
        <lb ed="#V" n="4"/><quote xml:id="bHY6yh-e09874-Qd1e352">Quottidie niorimur: quottidie enim 
               demit<lb ed="#V" n="5" break="no"/>titur aliqua pars vite. Et tunc quoque cum
        <lb ed="#V" n="6"/>crescimus vita decrescit. Ultima hora qua
        <lb ed="#V" n="7"/>esse desinimus<!--u flipped--> non sola mortem facit: sed
        <lb ed="#V" n="8"/>sola consummat.</quote>
          </p>
          <p xml:id="bHY6yh-e09874-d1e367"> 
      / <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-e09874-Rd1e414">Libro 15. epistola 4.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-e09874-Qd1e369">Omnia 
               morta<lb ed="#V" n="9" break="no"/>lium opera mortali a te damnata sunt.</quote>
          </p>
          <p xml:id="bHY6yh-e09874-d1e375"> 
      / <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-e09874-Rd1e424">
               Li<lb ed="#V" n="10" break="no"/>bro. 20. et finali. epistola 3.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-e09874-Qd1e377">Quottidie propius ab 
               vlti<lb ed="#V" n="11" break="no"/>mo stamus: et illo vnde nobis cadendum est
        <lb ed="#V" n="12"/>hora nos omnis impellit.</quote>
          </p>
          <p xml:id="bHY6yh-e09874-d1e387"> 
      / <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-e09874-Rd1e439">6. capitulo.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-e09874-Qd1e389">Fluunt 
               di<lb ed="#V" n="13" break="no"/>es et irreparabilis vita decurrit.</quote>
          </p>
          <p xml:id="bHY6yh-e09874-d1e395">
        <lb ed="#V" n="14"/>¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-e09874-Rd1e451">Seneca de remediis fortuitorum. capitulo i.</ref>
        <lb ed="#V" n="15"/><quote xml:id="bHY6yh-e09874-Qd1e399">Mos omnia abscidit. Mors omnia 
               de<lb ed="#V" n="16" break="no"/>uorat.</quote>
          </p>
          <p xml:id="bHY6yh-e09874-d1e407"> 
      / <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-e09874-Rd1e463">2. capitulo.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-e09874-Qd1e409">Peregrinatio est vita hoc: cum
        <lb ed="#V" n="17"/>multum ambulaueris demum redeundum
        <lb ed="#V" n="18"/>est. Quod ceperit desinit.</quote>
          </p>
          <p xml:id="bHY6yh-e09874-d1e417"> 
      / <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-e09874-Rd1e476">5. capitulo.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-e09874-Qd1e419">
               Adolescen<lb ed="#V" n="19" break="no"/>tes et impuberes eadem fati necessitas 
               du<lb ed="#V" n="20" break="no"/>cit.</quote>
          </p>
          <p xml:id="bHY6yh-e09874-d1e428"> 
      / <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-e09874-Rd1e488">16. capitulo.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-e09874-Qd1e430">Non est idem ordo fati quod et etatis</quote>
          </p>
          <p xml:id="bHY6yh-e09874-d1e434">
        <lb ed="#V" n="21"/>¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-e09874-Rd1e498">Lucanus. libro 7.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-e09874-Qd1e438">Capit omnia telus
        <lb ed="#V" n="22"/>Que genuit.</quote>
          </p>
          <p xml:id="bHY6yh-e09874-d1e444">
        <lb ed="#V" n="23"/>¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-e09874-Rd1e510">Maximianus.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-e09874-Qd1e448">Ortus cuncta suos 
               repe<lb ed="#V" n="24" break="no"/>tunt matremque requirunt.
        <lb ed="#V" n="25"/>Et redit ad nihilum quod fuit ante nihil.
        <lb ed="#V" n="26"/>Omnibus est eadem leti via non tamen vnus
        <lb ed="#V" n="27"/>Est vite cunctis exitiique modus.
        <lb ed="#V" n="28"/>Huc puer atque senex paritur iuuenesque feruntur.
        <lb ed="#V" n="29"/>Hic par diuitibus pauper egenus erit.</quote>
          </p>
          <p xml:id="bHY6yh-e09874-d1e465">
        <lb ed="#V" n="30"/>¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-e09874-Rd1e533">Boetius de consolatione. libro 2. capiutlo 14.</ref>
        <lb ed="#V" n="31"/><quote xml:id="bHY6yh-e09874-Qd1e469">Mors spernit altam gloriam:
        <lb ed="#V" n="32"/>Inuoluit humilem pariter et celsum caput:
        <lb ed="#V" n="33"/>Equatque summis infima.</quote>
          </p>
          <p xml:id="bHY6yh-e09874-d1e479">
        <lb ed="#V" n="34"/>¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-e09874-Rd1e549">Isydorus solliloquiorum. libro i. capitulo 10.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-e09874-Qd1e483">
               Quot<lb ed="#V" n="35" break="no"/>tidie dies vltimus appropinquat. Uitam
        <lb ed="#V" n="36"/>nostram quottidie dies aufert: Quottidie ad
        <lb ed="#V" n="37"/>finem tendimus. Ad mortem quottidie 
               pro<lb ed="#V" n="38" break="no"/>peramus.</quote>
          </p>
          <p xml:id="bHY6yh-e09874-d1e495">
        <lb ed="#V" n="39"/>¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-e09874-Rd1e568">Bernardus in libro contemptus mundi.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-e09874-Qd1e499">Mors
        <lb ed="#V" n="40"/>resecat mors omne necat quod carne creatur.
        <lb ed="#V" n="41"/>Magnificos praemit et modicos cunctis dominatur.
        <lb ed="#V" n="42"/>Nobilium tenet imperium: nulli reueretur.
        <lb ed="#V" n="43"/>Tam ducibus quam principibus communis habetur.
        <lb ed="#V" n="44"/>Mors inuuenes rapit atque senes nulli miseretur.
        <lb ed="#V" n="45"/>Sed quid plura loquar: nulli mors impia parcit. <!--326.xml-->
          <cb ed="#V" n="b"/>
        <lb ed="#V" n="46"/>Non euadit inops nec qui marsupia facit.
        <lb ed="#V" n="47"/>Non igitur cesses que bona sunt operari.
        <lb ed="#V" n="48"/>Nam mors non cessat tibi nocte dieque minari.</quote>
          </p>
          <p xml:id="bHY6yh-e09874-d1e527">
        <lb ed="#V" n="49"/>¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-e09874-Rd1e601">Prouerbia vulgaria.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-e09874-Qd1e531">Cosi more el gran 
               signo<lb ed="#V" n="50" break="no"/>re cum fa olauoraore.</quote>
            </p>
